name: World Worth Winning
description: The world is hanging in limbo as free speech is politicized, our movements tracked by big tech companies, and extremists like Elizabeth Warren have suggested taxing unrealized capital gains. In such a time, decentralized economics were essential to the aspirations of the entrepreneurs of the day. Liquidity pools on never before seen financial institutions of the likes of sebuh.net, intertwined in blockchain atrophy we forged ourselves a free layer of political neutrality. We needed to block the ads from corporations selling us goods that would lower our quality of living if we paid for them. At last, we have our peace of mind, but will it endure the destructive forces of the International Monetary Fund and the World Economic Forum?
